dct_title_s: Map of Summit and vicinity : "Popular Trading Centre" also "The City of Beautiful Homes"., New Jersey.
dct_description_sm: Copyright 1940 by Ray S. Opdyake. Oriented with north toward the upper left. Panel title. "Popular Trading Centre" also "The City of Beautiful Homes." Map shows radial distance. Includes street index, historical notes and photographs. "Copyright 1940 by Ray S. Opdyke." "Issued thru the cooperation of the Chamber of Commerce of Summit, N.J."--Panel. Illustrated local businesses with addresses and phone numbers on verso.
